name: ACURA

name: AGRALE

name: ALEKO

name: ALFA ROMEO

name: ARO

name: ASIA

name: ASIA CAMION

name: BAIC

name: BELAVTOMAZ

name: BERTONE

name: BLAC

name: BMW

name: BUIK

name: CHEVROLET CAM.

name: DACIA

name: DAEWOO

name: DAIHATSU

name: DAIHATSU CAMION
